---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="About" description="About Mariana Costa, data engineer and open-source contributor.">
  <div class="about-page">
    <section class="about-hero">
      <div class="about-avatar">
        <img src="/img/profile.jpg" alt="Mariana Costa" width="88" height="88" />
      </div>
      <h1>Mariana Costa</h1>
      <p class="about-bio">
        Data engineer interested in Spark, lakehouse architectures, data visualization,
        and open-source contributions. Currently exploring LanceDB internals
        and Spark UI optimization.
      </p>
      <div class="about-links">
        <a href="https://github.com/mrncstt" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/mrncstt/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section">
      <h2>What I do</h2>
      <p>
        I work with data pipelines, lakehouse architectures, and distributed systems.
        Most of my day-to-day involves PySpark on Databricks, but I'm also drawn to
        the edges: contributing to open-source projects, building visualizations,
        and writing about what I learn along the way.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section">
      <h2>This blog</h2>
      <p>
        A mix of technical deep-dives, short TIL notes, and the occasional travel post.
        I write in both English and Portuguese depending on the topic and audience.
        Everything here reflects things I've actually built, broken, or figured out.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section">
      <h2>Elsewhere</h2>
      <p>
        You can find my code on <a href="https://github.com/mrncstt" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>
        and connect with me on <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/mrncstt/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>.
        I'm also occasionally active in data engineering communities and open-source projects.
      </p>
    </section>

    <p class="about-disclaimer">
      All opinions are my own.
    </p>
  </div>
</Layout>
